## ðŸŒ Endpoint API

| Method | URL | Auth | Keterangan |
|--------|-----|------|-----------|
| GET | `/api/chat/health` | âŒ | Cek status API |
| POST | `/api/chat` | âœ… Sanctum | Kirim pesan ke chatbot |

### Request Body (POST /api/chat)
```json
{
  "message": "Saya butuh jasa desain logo"
}
```

### Response Sukses
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "reply": "Kami punya banyak vendor desain grafis yang siap membantu!",
  "usage": {
    "prompt_tokens": 45,
    "completion_tokens": 28
  }
}
```

